description.fr: {CharacterName:596} poursuit {Summoning:1557} jusque dans le Donjon Chafer\_; le Shushu ne doit pas s'échapper\_!
description.en: {CharacterName:596} has followed {Summoning:1557} into the Chafer Dungeon. The Shushu mustn't get away!
description.es: {CharacterName:596} persigue a {Summoning:1557} hasta la Mazmorra de los Chafers; ¡el fab'huritu no puede escaparse!
description.de: {CharacterName:596} verfolgt {Summoning:1557} bis zum Chafer-Dungeon. Jetzt sitzt der Shushu in der Falle!
description.pt: {CharacterName:596} perseguiu {Summoning:1557} até o Calabouço Chafer. Agora o Shushu não tem como escapar!

descriptionFinished.fr: {Summoning:1557} s'est avéré être un Shushu fuyard\_; après une course poursuite à travers le donjon, {CharacterName:596} est finalement parvenu à s'en débarrasser.
descriptionFinished.en: {Summoning:1557} turned out to have a knack for running away. After chasing the Shushu through the dungeon, {CharacterName:596} finally managed to get rid of him.
descriptionFinished.es: {Summoning:1557} ha resultado ser un fab'huritu fugitivo; tras una persecución a través de la mazmorra, {CharacterName:596} por fin ha conseguido deshacerse de él.
descriptionFinished.de: {Summoning:1557} hat sich als überaus wendiger Shushu erwiesen. Nach einer halsbrecherischen Verfolgungsjagd quer durch den Dungeon konnte {CharacterName:596} ihn endlich stellen und erledigen.
descriptionFinished.pt: {Summoning:1557} se mostrou ser um Shushu fujão. Depois de uma rápida perseguição pelo calabouço, {CharacterName:596} finalmente conseguiu se livrar dele.
